08:43.632 --> 08:46.633
MR. ROSENSWIEG:
That poor walleyed bastard.

08:50.331 --> 08:52.067
(pen scratching on paper)

08:52.067 --> 08:53.970
(sighs)

09:05.247 --> 09:07.654
Rémy Martin. Louis XIII.

09:07.654 --> 09:09.920
Christmas gift from
the Board of Trustees.

09:09.920 --> 09:12.054
Oh, how generous of them.

09:12.054 --> 09:14.155
Thank you again
for doing this, Hunham.

09:14.155 --> 09:16.630
I wouldn't have asked
if it weren't an emergency.

09:16.630 --> 09:19.226
Oh, Mr. Endicott's mother, right.

09:19.226 --> 09:20.997
What a tragedy.

09:20.997 --> 09:24.297
It's not as though you had plans
to leave campus anyway.

09:24.297 --> 09:27.300
And, of course, there's a nice
little bonus in it for you.

09:27.300 --> 09:31.777
Well... (sighs) <i>"Non nobis
solum nati sumus,"</i> I suppose.

09:33.979 --> 09:36.815
"Not for ourselves alone
are we born."

09:39.050 --> 09:41.017
I'm guessing that's Cicero.

09:41.017 --> 09:42.953
Cicero, yes.

09:42.953 --> 09:45.626
(chuckling): Very good, Hardy.
You remembered.

09:53.031 --> 09:55.526
