My dad's going to flip out.

13:50.332 --> 13:53.632
(students murmuring)

13:55.141 --> 13:57.438
All right. All right.

13:57.438 --> 13:59.671
Uh, in the spirit of the season,

13:59.671 --> 14:01.442
I suppose the most
constructive way

14:01.442 --> 14:03.378
of dealing with
your shortcomings

14:03.378 --> 14:07.019
is to offer a makeup exam.

14:07.019 --> 14:09.615
