grades stand.

15:27.693 --> 15:30.135
(students groaning, murmuring)

15:30.135 --> 15:31.697
Uh, excuse me, sir.

15:31.697 --> 15:34.667
I think, uh, we all liked
the first option better.

15:34.667 --> 15:36.768
What'd you say the guy's
name was? Uh, Demosthe-who?

15:36.768 --> 15:39.210
Of course, I still expect you
to be familiar with chapter six

15:39.210 --> 15:42.378
upon your return,
so pack those textbooks, boys.

15:42.378 --> 15:44.380
And if displeased,

15:44.380 --> 15:47.482
take it up with
your champion-- Mr. Tully.

15:48.419 --> 15:50.056
