17:15.273 --> 17:18.144
who know not
the loving kindness of God.

17:18.144 --> 17:20.311
Sorry to hear about
your mother, Endicott.

17:20.311 --> 17:21.741
What?

17:21.741 --> 17:23.809
Oh. Yes.

17:23.809 --> 17:25.217
Thank you.

17:25.217 --> 17:27.285
Yeah. We're all pulling for her.

17:27.285 --> 17:28.979
PRIEST:
...and your grace.

17:28.979 --> 17:32.983
And finally, let us pray
for the soul of Curtis Lamb,

17:32.983 --> 17:35.656
Barton class of 1969.

17:35.656 --> 17:38.626
Just this year,
Curtis gave his life valiantly

17:38.626 --> 17:40.826
